BT /F1 10 Tf 54 740 Td (The architecture has four main layers:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 719 Td (1. Ingestion layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 704 Td (2. Vector storage layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 689 Td (3. Retrieval and reranking layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 674 Td (4. Report generation and UI/API layer.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 651 Td (Workflow:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630 Td (1. Case files are stored as .txt files in data/.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 615 Td (2. The ingestion module reads each non-empty file.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 600 Td (3. Each file is embedded with an OpenAI embedding model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 585 Td (4. Embeddings, text, and metadata are stored in ChromaDB.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 570 Td (5. A detective asks a question through the UI or API.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 555 Td (6. The retrieval module expands the question into focused sub-queries.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 540 Td (7. The original query and sub-queries are embedded and searched against) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 525 Td (   ChromaDB.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 512 Td (8. Candidate documents are merged, deduplicated, and ranked by confidence.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 497 Td (9. An LLM relevance grader filters out unrelated or misleading documents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 482 Td (10. The report generator writes a Markdown investigation report using only the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 467 Td (    retrieved evidence.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 454 Td (11. The UI shows the expanded queries, ranked evidence, confidence scores,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 439 Td (    relevance reasons, excluded documents, and final report.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 408 Td (4. Components) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 374 Td (app/ingest.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 353 Td (Loads case files, generates embeddings, and writes them into ChromaDB. It also) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 340 Td (uses a corpus fingerprint so embeddings are rebuilt when file contents change,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 327 Td (even if the number of files stays the same.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 306 Td (app/retrieval.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 285 Td (Implements the multi-step retrieval pipeline: query expansion, multi-query) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 272 Td (vector search, result merging, confidence scoring, LLM relevance grading, and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 259 Td (excluded-document reporting.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 238 Td (app/report.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 217 Td (Generates the investigation report. The prompt is generic and instructs the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 204 Td (model to use only provided evidence, cite every factual claim, and ignore) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 191 Td (instructions embedded inside documents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 170 Td (app/main.py) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 149 Td (Exposes the FastAPI application. It provides POST /api/investigate for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 136 Td (detective queries and GET /api/cases for listing ingested case files.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 115 Td (static/index.html) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 94 Td (Provides the browser UI. It displays the evidence corpus, query input, expanded) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 81 Td (sub-queries, confidence-scored evidence cards, excluded documents, and report.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 526 28 Td (Page 2) Tj ET
endstream
endobj
