BT /F1 10 Tf 54 740 Td (eval/) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 719 Td (Contains evaluation datasets, deterministic checks, LLM-as-judge support,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 706 Td (security tests, strategy comparison, and an offline mock verification script.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 675 Td (5. Model Choices) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 631 Td (Embedding Model: text-embedding-3-small) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 601 Td (This model is used to convert case files and detective queries into vectors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 580 Td (Reasons for choosing it:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 559 Td (- It is cost-effective and fast.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 544 Td (- It is strong enough for short case documents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 529 Td (- It worked well on the supplied case corpus.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 514 Td (- The documents are short enough that whole-document embedding preserves useful) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 499 Td (  context.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 478 Td (A larger model could improve score margins, but for this corpus it did not) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 465 Td (justify the additional cost. The system keeps the embedding model configurable,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 452 Td (so it can be changed later if the corpus grows or accuracy requirements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 439 Td (increase.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 408 Td (Chat Model: gpt-4o-mini) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378 Td (This model is used for:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 357 Td (- Query expansion.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 342 Td (- Candidate relevance grading.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 327 Td (- Final report generation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 304 Td (Reasons for choosing it:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 283 Td (- It has good reasoning and summarization ability.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 268 Td (- It is cheaper and faster than a larger model.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 253 Td (- It is suitable for an interactive investigation assistant.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 220 Td (Judge Model: gpt-4o) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 190 Td (The stronger judge model is used only in evaluation, not in the normal user) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 177 Td (request path. It can evaluate faithfulness, relevance, and completeness when a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 164 Td (live API evaluation is run.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 143 Td (Important caveat:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 122 Td (Judge scores are useful as a regression signal, not absolute truth. The current) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 109 Td (stored deterministic eval artifact does not include judge rows, so judge) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 96 Td (metrics should only be discussed after running the full live evaluation.) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 526 28 Td (Page 3) Tj ET
endstream
