stream
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 740 Td (The multi-step approach improves recall by searching multiple angles and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 727 Td (improves precision by adding an LLM relevance grader.) Tj ET
BT /F2 12 Tf 54 696 Td (Justification From Evaluation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 666 Td (The strategy comparison showed:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 645 Td (- Single-step top-1 had 81% recall overall and only 50% recall on) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 630 Td (  multi-document questions.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 617 Td (- Naive top-k retrieval improved recall but had poor precision because it) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 602 Td (  included too many distractors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 589 Td (- The full multi-step pipeline retrieved all expected evidence on the small) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 574 Td (  supplied fixture while reducing distractor leakage.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 553 Td (Important framing:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 532 Td (The 100% recall result is only on the supplied eight-query fixture. It should) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 519 Td (not be presented as real-world accuracy. It means the implementation passes the) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 506 Td (assignment scenario and has no known regression on that small labeled set.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 475 Td (8. Ranking, Confidence, and Explainability) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 441 Td (Each retrieved document has:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 420 Td (- Source filename.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 405 Td (- Confidence score.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 390 Td (- Query or sub-query that matched it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 375 Td (- Relevance reason from the grader.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 360 Td (- Full text preview.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 337 Td (This gives detectives transparency. They can see not only the final report, but) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 324 Td (also the evidence path that produced it.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 303 Td (Documents that are rejected are not hidden. They are shown separately as) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 290 Td (excluded documents with reasons. This matters because the corpus intentionally) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 277 Td (contains misleading information.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 256 Td (Confidence score limitation:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 235 Td (The score is a retrieval similarity score, not a probability that the document) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 222 Td (is true. This distinction is important in a real investigation system.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 191 Td (9. Report Generation) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 157 Td (The report generator receives:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 136 Td (- The detective's original question.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 121 Td (- Only the retrieved evidence documents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 106 Td (- Source filenames and confidence scores.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 83 Td (The report prompt instructs the model to:) Tj ET
BT /F1 8 Tf 526 28 Td (Page 5) Tj ET
endstream
