stream
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 740 Td (Operational edge case:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 719 Td (- Replacing case files with a different corpus of the same size. This is handled) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 704 Td (  by corpus fingerprinting so stale embeddings are not reused.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 673 Td (15. Limitations) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 639 Td (The main limitation is evaluation size. The supplied fixture is small, so a) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 626 Td (perfect retrieval score should not be treated as real-world reliability.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 605 Td (Other limitations:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 584 Td (- LLM grading is probabilistic.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 569 Td (- Similarity scores are not truth probabilities.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 554 Td (- The current deployment is local and does not include authentication,) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 539 Td (  authorization, or audit logging.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 526 Td (- The judge model is useful but not a substitute for human review.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 511 Td (- Exact generated wording may vary between runs.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 478 Td (16. Production Improvements) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 444 Td (If this were moved toward production, I would add:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 423 Td (- Larger blind holdout evaluation sets.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 408 Td (- Negative queries where the correct answer is "insufficient evidence.") Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 393 Td (- Near-duplicate distractors.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 378 Td (- Conflicting evidence documents.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 363 Td (- Human reviewer feedback and override tracking.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 348 Td (- Hybrid lexical plus vector retrieval.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 333 Td (- Optional cross-encoder reranking.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 318 Td (- Stronger post-generation citation verification.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 303 Td (- Auth, audit logs, and access controls.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 288 Td (- Observability for latency, cost, retrieval quality, and report quality.) Tj ET
BT /F2 15 Tf 54 255 Td (17. Recommended Presentation Flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 221 Td (Start with the goal:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 200 Td ("This is a case-agnostic RAG assistant for detectives. It retrieves evidence) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 187 Td (and generates a cited report, but it does not rely on case-specific prompt) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54 174 Td (knowledge.") Tj ET
